## Instructions
1. Identify the most important entities mentioned in the article (up to 20).
2. For each entity provide: name, type (person/place/organization/concept/event/other), wikidata_id (if known or inferable), first_mention_context (the sentence where it first appears), and relation_to_subject (how it relates to the article's main topic).
3. Exclude the article's own subject from the list.

## Output Format
JSON only:
{
  "entities_extracted": [
    {
      "name": "string",
      "type": "string|null",
      "wikidata_id": "string|null",
      "first_mention_context": "string|null",
      "relation_to_subject": "string|null"
    }
  ]
}
